{"hd5827babgcda9g4d04gb3fagc9e92ac8e62d": ["*You spot a man crouching between the shelves - just as he spots you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "633fe4ec-5ca8-a443-c567-96dcb76a1764"], "h9ca74d23g6688g43c1ga91fgecb19b4b4ee4": ["Bugger.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "c515eab3-ace0-4831-afeb-a608af90276e"], "h2453105aga0d2g47cdgac2dg54003c6e04cb": ["<i>Recite Rugan's pass-phrase: 'Little serpent, long shadow'.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "17b19434-b961-cdfe-6151-4201b3e653a2"], "hab9a021dg8c65g44ddg9f54gf2930d676a4b": ["Gah, Helm's <i>orbs</i>. Thought you were Flaming Fist. ", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "49635ee0-f215-f31c-f19f-83510794a4b5"], "hf24a38b4gcbeeg4759ga49ag9d7d6981a528": ["Down you go, then. They'll be on us soon, so if you're looking to trade you'd best be quick.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "007fde22-826c-05ca-ad20-5e9729ffac1f"], "h54a3f5e9gc03eg474dgbdc7ge1ba896f90da": ["Entrance is hidden behind the wardrobe - here's the key.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "9613d1aa-8c88-0f33-0b23-4e2dd29af352"], "h5821c767g4db8g4435g95b1g4ba2c88633eb": ["Entrance is hidden behind the wardrobe. You'll find a key in one of the crates.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "0050e0cf-6b14-d983-a987-402ce78c5029"], "hff98c1d1g081fg4ec8g8b90g1014d7492306": ["I'm with Zarys - <i>do not cast that spell</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "00642ed1-307b-2c44-0dc2-2f98176b5aa8"], "hd72f173bg4e96g4911gb935g43c3317aad48": ["One of our own, eh? All right, down you go.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "7209c31a-8a8d-5226-5e71-f04f54728791"], "hddb4cedfg0882g4f93g9871g24e4295396f2": ["Wait - listen!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "e026a6a5-bdf0-276b-064c-378083e758b2"], "h66699f2cg3be5g4dccg9161g0e47da79700e": ["*He freezes, waiting on your next word.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "799ba900-118a-9e07-5602-62deeed078f0"], "h66d7393ag6c97g4640g9f10gd644b74d3d7d": ["Careful. You won't kill me, but you <i>will </i>make me mad.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "74c80e0c-8304-6737-8508-921d88fc9916"], "hbde622e2gb168g42cbg86bfg31ea31044672": ["Right, look - if it's business you're about, then be about it. Flaming Fist could be on us any minute.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "2a7b0738-350f-92bb-c482-e8fbefcb4bc5"], "h0bab8e5dgeb74g478fga09cga3443024ca1b": ["Down you go - entrance is behind the wardrobe. Here's the key.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "7be80a47-25fe-0998-1d1f-c148eb6a810c"], "h1b5ab08agd26ag4a4egb37ag77e2bcfdda9c": ["Down you go - entrance is behind the wardrobe. You'll find a key in one of the crates.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "c42f1f91-186a-2e34-f0c5-e89fe191d098"], "h44c454e4g9c55g4535ga0e6g2be9d3691d0f": ["Just calm down - I'm not here to fight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "b6a1b9e2-fff8-6fa7-8b3c-095f7c44945a"], "h47953d76g5d0fg4afdga231g11025e89e45c": ["That ain't the pass-phrase!", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "d129f96f-698e-0957-8079-9e15bb074cb8"], "hd50c13cdgc2f5g4e81gbeabg098214e83001": ["That ain't the pass-phrase!", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "14e89ebc-aa6b-2872-9b27-77f94e6f9d20"], "h6dab45d6g8546g4344g8dcfg295dbce163a5": ["This is all pretty crude, as traps go - you'll probably kill us both.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "c9b7c310-5be6-38a6-8961-6bc55852be2c"], "h9665fa8agc381g4d5aga2a5g7baa0dfebf4f": ["You can cast the spell, but we'll die together.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "2b15d6b6-e7b6-9d01-a796-994ce7e5d28b"], "h93f249bfge9fdg47e1g8a66g6d84abf7ed76": ["That spell, in close quarters? You're going to hurt yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "f3d31959-5f58-e59d-ad32-246d4d53f0f0"], "h1a2a810egcda5g420bg8a18gcb50147ed7d6": ["... let's say I'd rather not fight, then. What's your business down here?", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "ab86865f-c41c-2a64-44b4-972b7f792965"], "h9adb9388g8e92g458dg88d0g4709f57600c7": ["I just want to trade.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "3f1f28e5-b2b2-a725-0e26-6e47884c403e"], "h7be3cc41g961bg472bgbd76ga172516c2c86": ["Your timing ain't the best, but I'm sure Zarys won't turn down a deal. Down you go, then.", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "d1e2f165-9299-6112-4ecf-87d6fa6878e3"], "ha6a2c7e0gf9d4g4148gbe6cg33751ffe5b38": ["<i>Flick out a single hand-sign: 'profit'.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "e49ac53f-d50c-cb88-4ef4-caa47abcc7be"], "he93d4c4agfc48g40e1g8557gbda64558caf5": ["<i>Attack him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "57e88f37-f5a2-17b5-f2da-859320b94aae"], "hb2c91734g0d30g42cbg8bc5gb64dd990ba72": ["<i>Read his mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "84e0430a-b389-e393-5585-fbf342f4d85a"], "ha8d8cec3g1f5cg4fb6g92dcg4d9c7fe44ae1": ["<i>'Little serpent, long shadow.' Don't want to die. 'Little serpent, long shadow.' Just say it!</i>", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "e624aec8-9fff-58d6-2ab2-ea4ecea174d1"], "h7e34120dge21eg42acg854eg0f820b9a3228": ["I know the pass-phrase: 'Little serpent, long shadow'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "9221989e-e5ac-cdb7-a0ee-e0268d69c0fe"], "h8492e5c3g42e6g4bbegbea8g0107b143dd3a": ["Stay out of my head! ", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "4eae8d75-5df7-7ecc-b678-289ce21cfba9"], "he6c2555bgd226g4659g944dg197a9ce1fa63": ["B-burn, bastard!", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "3e5320a0-f741-91dc-c720-f18c4203c36c"], "hbcb53b10g8283g4395ga127g148064dfd9dc": ["Zarys! ZARYS, HELP!", "85e11906-83ea-4f2f-b5cb-f1e2a6710513", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "14559e89-4fbe-2e1a-4ae9-95c8c5c8e3bf"], "hdee3f38agc5c8g404dg9f72g2e09b4386e33": ["<i>Prepare to attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "5f1a724e-bf0d-fc97-8d64-e69c1058aa8b"], "h9e6691e9g8faeg4e38ga5a6gc0443ade0a84": ["*A human man awaits you, a spell crackling at his fingertips.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "7d1a70e8-ac55-4b7d-a2f1-dba9686a1b40"], "h1ba0af6eg543cg4ab5gaa56g10607ffcbdbb": ["<i>Recite Rugan's pass-phrase: 'Little serpent, long shadow'.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "1c31357f-e241-b49b-d652-c6ff07c88790"], "hf494dfb6g6b6bg48c0gb1a7g243dc9a97e39": ["Wait!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "159f2471-969a-cc16-c1b1-cddc14c257c0"], "h3a84f3f7g81e1g4854gb73fga72903937f0d": ["*You spot a man crouching between the shelves - just as he spots you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "c909de7d-d7eb-f1aa-fbb1-5564f1236585"], "hd6db82dbgaf3ag4467gb8b6g772366b1d97f": ["*A human man awaits you, a spell crackling at his fingertips.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_EscapingZhentarim.html", "fb953d8e-ba3a-ecd4-2969-fe9dc2a6f908"]}